summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Warrant Avenue from Roy Street to a manhole 120 ft south to the south margin of Harrison Street et al, in the City of Seattle, by constructing sewer under Ordinance No. 19249, creating Local Improvement District No. 1856 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
